= Legal & Compliance =

(% class="box infomessage" %)
(((
**FactHarbor maintains independence and user protection through a formal legal and financial framework.**
Our commitment to open source (**AGPL-3.0 / MIT**) and our "20% Donor Rule" ensure that the project remains a transparent public asset.

**Project Repository:** [[FactHarbor on GitHub>>https://github.com/robertschaub/FactHarbor]]
)))

